      "order" : 2380,
      "type" : "TextML",
      "value" : "<p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      Walibi, the amusement park for the whole family!\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      \r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      The famous Radja River, the terrifying train through the mines and many \r\n      more attractions for a family trip unlike any other &#8230;\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      \r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      Enchanting merry-go-rounds for the younger set, and emotional thrills \r\n      for the bold!\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      \r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      Show lovers vibrate to the sound of W.A.B. guitars or rock to the fast \r\n      pace of the Skunx. Better still, you'll love a spellbinding musical \r\n      battle!\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      \r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      An extraordinary experience to enjoy with your family and friends!\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      \r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0\">\r\n      <i>Further information about the vicinity: <a href=\"http://www.mtab.be\">www.mtab.be</a> \r\n      / +32 10 23 03 52</i>\r\n    </p>"
